<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="Support%20Care%20Cancer"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Computerized patient reported symptom assessment in radiotherapy: a pilot randomized, controlled trial</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Fromme%20EK"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Erik K Fromme</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Erik K Fromme</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, MCR, FAAHPM</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Mail Code: L586, Division of Hematology &amp; Medical Oncology, OHSU Knight Cancer Institute, Oregon Health &amp; Science University, Portland, OR 97239, Phone: 503-494-3152, Fax: 503-494-3257, frommee@ohsu.edu</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Fromme%20EK"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Erik K Fromme</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>✉</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Holliday%20EB"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Emma B Holliday</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Emma B Holliday</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>Division of Radiation Oncology, The University of Texas MD Anderson Cancer Center, 1515 Holcombe Blvd Unit 97, Houston, Texas 78240, Phone: 210-854-5399, emmaholliday@gmail.com</div>
