<h3>
<span class="name western">Lillian M Nail</span>, <span class="degrees">PhD, RN</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>School of Nursing, Oregon Health &amp; Science University</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Nail%20LM"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Lillian M Nail</span></a>
</div>
